Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: New York blackout
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b0407j00
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 17 Jul 1977
New York blacked out during power outage. Shops looted in darkened streets. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.